class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4ad089ab0a5a202ac446fd0fe53b6fcfa84a4d","tid":332172,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熊本城收左皮喎</blockquote><br />\n之前有間九州橫斷特急 <br />\n真心好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜仲未搞返掂</blockquote><br />\n上年3月去搭咗<br />\n4月就地震<br />\n可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7ecd7555f166cf38e241b36dc4ce7bb35a2a83","tid":332172,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:23:46.000Z","msg":"都係直接答樓主啦<br />\n其實咁真係好趕時間<br />\n<br />\n如果你用公共交通<br />\n根據yahoo個乗換案内<br />\n由博多站去到阿蘇站<br />\n都要最少差不多3粒鐘<br />\n仲要再搭巴士上阿蘇山<br />\n你預中午先上到山<br />\n我諗你唔會上去一陣就走咁戇鳩掛<br />\n你應該唔會有時間返熊本睇熊本城<br />\n所以你個plan應該唔work<br />\n<br />\n如果係自駕的話<br />\n早啲出發應該都可以嘅<br />\n但係都算趕時間囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbetween熊本城未整好<br />\n不過出面睇都係好宏偉嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2080e2fd6e1550186dd048d85895db528a08df9c","tid":332172,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:24:53.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"aef6ef9bf30ce07006a3dd4cf8f5771272fce60a","tid":332172,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個月先去完<br />\n<br />\n阿蘇火山無纜車<br />\n<br />\n基本上無咩野睇到...</blockquote><br />\n冇纜車？咁點上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad064c80b12d60620224573710b4526b99bfb3fc","tid":332172,"uid":121562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係直接答樓主啦<br />\n其實咁真係好趕時間<br />\n<br />\n如果你用公共交通<br />\n根據yahoo個乗換案内<br />\n由博多站去到阿蘇站<br />\n都要最少差不多3粒鐘<br />\n仲要再搭巴士上阿蘇山<br />\n你預中午先上到山<br />\n我諗你唔會上去一陣就走咁戇鳩掛<br />\n你應該唔會有時間返熊本睇熊本城<br 